  m_Name: ABrokenFishingRodDialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  resourceName: A Broken Fishing Rod
  displayName: 
  icon: {fileID: 0}
  iconBackgroundImage: {fileID: 0}
  description: 
  useRegionalDescription: 0
  resourceDescriptionProfile: 
  automatic: 0
  repeatable: 0
  audioProfileName: 
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Oh no!


      That rod you are carrying looks like it belonged
      to someone I know.'
    nextOption: That's why I am here
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The initials on the rod, SAL, indicate that this belonged to SwimALot,
      a champion explorer in our ranks.


      He left on a search to find the Great
      GoldenFish in the mythical Lost City Of Eldorado.'
    nextOption: What happened to him?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Nothing bad I hope, but SwimALot would never leave his fishing
      rod behind.


      I hope he didn''t get captured.'
    nextOption: Who would capture him?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The city is rumored to be sunken off the coast.


      To get
      to the coast requires travelling through the Glowing Forest, home of the Goblins.'
    nextOption: That sounds dangerous
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It gets worse!


      Beyond the forest is the Mystical Village,
      which has beem walled off behind a magical shield for millenia.


      The
      channelers there are hostile to all outsiders.'
    nextOption: Uh Oh
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Thank you for returning his rod to me.


      He has been gone
      quite some time and at least now we know that he may be in trouble.


      In
      honor of his dedication to fishing, I would like to pass on the art to you.'
    nextOption: Thank you, that sounds quite useful
